<br>
<br>
Verrant needs to look into opening the path of the Mage a little more. As it stands now I have been seeing at the endgame we become conjour mages summoning t-rods that have a great and fearsome pet in are pocket that we can farm with &lt;JK on the farming thing&gt; They molded us into one path and that needs to be fixed<br>
